parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlHuClNo6.Ugh!... Ring the bells! He may be blinded, but he can hear you!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DmAnOp.Nice try, but now the Toma is mine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Daemalius is blinded, but he can hear you! Don’t get too close!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoEx.Push the stones into place. I think you can trap him from the sides!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.He stole the Toma… Maybe Henry should have helped take the chest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlAnEx.Leave the Toma where it lays… Find Erica’s body... Make sure the soul and body become one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Evie! Where is Father Solomon? Where is Henry?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFrEx.Yeah, this part of the game isn’t finished yet.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.What the hell are you talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlEx.These things take time… But don’t worry, you’re going to love the next chapter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvHaEx.You get to be the star in the largest reverse gangbang ever created!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlEx.Well… It’s the largest one so far in this series.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlEx.Come back here in a couple weeks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvShOp.Woah! A personal portal! I’ve never seen one in person.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.Goodbye, Evie. Even though we are sworn enemies, you were quite helpful. I owe you my gratitude.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlEx.I’m a big fan of Earth. I’d hate to see it ruined by a loser demon like Daemalius.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Come on… Let’s not keep her waiting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvSaEx.I can’t save you this time, 1Hero… Your purpose has been served.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoCl^.So… This is the end of the line.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvSaEx.I’m sorry. But that portal won’t work for you… You have no Earthly body… It’s been blown to bits.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFrEx.Don’t worry, Henry. There are perks to being a soul trapped in Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnOp^.What good does that do here if I’m trapped?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFrEx.You’re not fully trapped… You can still visit Limbo!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrSaDe.I guess there’s no saving his body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFrEx.His body was turned into a fine mist.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvBaEx.You’d need a shell being to return to Earth… And I believe all of them are gone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFrEx.If you had the soul crystal, you could use that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvHaOp.Of course, Henry. How do you think I did it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.So… We just need the soul crystal?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.It’s in the evil chapel behind the church… Hopefully it’s still there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoWoCl.Let’s get the fuck out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoEx.We stopped him from taking the artifact, but… he may come back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.They chased after her body… We need to find her, and fast.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Lilith chased after Daemalius… He could come back at any moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.It’s over, Miss Deluna. We have it, and your contributions won’t go unpaid.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaDe.Does this mean you’ll hold up your end of our bargain?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Hey! No one’s taking that statue! We need to find the priest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.Don’t let your old man down, Canmore. Surely we can all agree that the statue is safer in the Guild’s hands.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnEx.You’re insane, Duncan. Madalyn isn’t going to share that treasure with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.Destroy it and keep the pieces! It’s a win for everyone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFlOp.Hahaha… An army is exactly what I intend to create!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaAg.Stay back! Don’t make me shoot you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.Join us! Let’s get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe.Fuck it… I guess I’m going back to jail.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlMaEx.What are you still doing here!? Find Erica near the altar! Now!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElBaEx.Let’s figure out a way to get past the monsters. We don’t want to set off any alarms.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.Bring us the soul crystal so we can save Henry. It should be in the dark chapel behind the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoCl.I can’t believe this is happening… What’s it like inside of a soul crystal?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFrEx.If you want to save Henry, you’ll need the soul crystal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvAnEx.Henry… Just go into the soul crystal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvAnOp.What were you expecting? Some kind of fancy ritual?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlDe.Needing my help until the very end, huh?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlOp.Goodbye, my love. See you when you get bored of living in a rock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvAnEx.Good luck using it, dumbass. It’s bound to someone else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlDe.Don’t you have a party to be going to?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFrEx.I’m Evie. It’s my job to know what’s supposed to come next.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.In Hell? What business do you have here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlOp.Hell’s a special place. There’s a lot going on here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElBaEx.Let’s figure out a way to get past them. We don’t want to set off any alarms.");
